swana would enjoy an afternoon off on Friday, August 9, 2024, to celebrate Tebogo's remarkable achievement at the ongoing 2024 Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 220, \"to\": 543, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 398, \"end\": 406, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.220338136681297e-15, \"text\": \"Botswana\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a press release\", \"from\": 223, \"to\": 238}, {\"ngram\": \"the Permanent Secretary\", \"from\": 275, \"to\": 298}, {\"ngram\": \"the President\", \"from\": 302, \"to\": 315}, {\"ngram\": \"Emmah A. Peloetletse\", \"from\": 317, \"to\": 337}, {\"ngram\": \"the President\", \"from\": 339, \"to\": 352}, {\"ngram\": \"all citizens\", \"from\": 368, \"to\": 380}, {\"ngram\": \"residents\", \"from\": 385, \"to\": 394}, {\"ngram\": \"an afternoon\", \"from\": 419, \"to\": 431}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday\", \"from\": 439, \"to\": 445}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 447, \"to\": 453}, {\"ngram\": \"Tebogo's remarkable achievement\", \"from\": 476, \"to\": 507}, {\"ngram\": \"the ongoing 2024 Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 511, \"to\": 542}]}, {\"sentence\": \"LEADERSHIP reports that Tebogo secured his place in history by winning the men's 200m gold medal, becoming not only the first Motswana but also the first African to claim this prestigious title.\", \"from\": 545, \"to\": 739, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 671, \"end\": 679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.136530245976377e-15, \"text\": \"Motswana\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"LEADERSHIP\", \"from\": 545, \"to\": 555}, {\"ngram\": \"Tebogo\", \"from\": 569, \"to\": 575}, {\"ngram\": \"his place\", \"from\": 584, \"to\": 593}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 597, \"to\": 604}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's 200m gold medal\", \"from\": 616, \"to\": 641}, {\"ngram\": \"the first African\", \"from\": 689, \"to\": 706}, {\"ngram\": \"this prestigious title\", \"from\": 716, \"to\": 738}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His victory has brought immense pride and joy to Botswana, prompting the President to recognise the achievement with a nationwide celebration.\", \"from\": 740, \"to\": 882, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 789, \"end\": 797, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.220338136681297e-15, \"text\": \"Botswana\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His victory\", \"from\": 740, \"to\": 751}, {\"ngram\": \"immense pride\", \"from\": 764, \"to\": 777}, {\"ngram\": \"joy\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 785}, {\"ngram\": \"the President\", \"from\": 809, \"to\": 822}, {\"ngram\": \"the achievement\", \"from\": 836, \"to\": 851}, {\"ngram\": \"a nationwide celebration\", \"from\": 857, \"to\": 881}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"His Excellency, Dr. Mokgweetsi Eric Keabetswe Masisi, President of the Republic of Botswana, hereby declares to the nation, that he has found it a fitting tribute to Mr. Letsile Tebogo, 'Botswana's Sensation', to grant Batswana and residents an afternoon day-off, on this very day, Friday the 9th August, 2024,\\\" the press release stated.\", \"from\": 886, \"to\": 1224, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 907, \"end\": 939, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mokgweetsi_Masisi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mokgweetsi Eric Keabetswe Masisi\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mokgweetsi_Masisi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mokgweetsi_Masisi\"}, {\"begin\": 1074, \"end\": 1082, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"score\